info.headline: Child Abduction Emergency issued June 13 at 9:45PM CDT by NWS El Paso
info.description: THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY. THE PRINCETON TEXAS POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR JAMYRA STRAWDER, A BLACK FEMALE who is 14 YEARS OLD. She is 5 FEET 7 INCHES tall, and weighs 140 POUNDS. She has BLACK HAIR with BROWN EYES. She was LAST SEEN WEARING A GRAY SWEATSHIRT, GRAY SWEATPANTS WITH WHITE STRIPE AND BLACK HOUSE SHOES. POLICE ARE SEARCHING FOR LEE CARTER THE THIRD, who is a BLACK MALE, 6 FEET 0 INCHES tall, weighing 203 POUNDS. He has BLACK HAIR, AND BROWN EYES. He was LAST SEEN WEARING UNKNOWN CLOTHING and has TATTOOS. Police are searching for him IN CONNECTION WITH THIS ABDUCTION. THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A BLACK, 2014, MERCEDES, E 35 WITH TX LICENSE PLATE: R N S 2 9 7 3. LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR IMMEDIATE DANGER. IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE PRINCETON POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 9 7 2 7 3 6 3 9 0 1.
